Tammy Petersen, News24 Cape Town - A man is on the run after he allegedly killed his ex-girlfriend's baby during a domestic dispute, police said on Wednesday. The seven-month-old infant was assaulted and died on Monday, Captain FC van Wyk said. "He allegedly killed the child after an argument with the mother." The man was believed to have been released from prison recently. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  